Teltoli / Rexon

*Rexon sees the pod fall, and he finishes of the meat he was eating. With a quick descision, the Fox/Wolf Hybrid sets off in that direction*

==================================

*Teltoli stiffens when she hears a female voice in her com, but she answers while ducking a blast* "I'm Teltoli, and I'm a Maximal!" *She ducks another blast, and transforms into robot form, keeping her energon blades at ready*

"And it would really really help if you could tell me where you are!"

*She shoots a look to her right, and sees Carnage fighting Tankorr. She giggles and then snarls, ducking another blast. This was the real fight.. her first one! And she wasn't so sure wether she should go ripping into them, the Predacons, or take them carefully. She was waiting for the reply*
